		<title>Visitor Activities at the Monastery</title>
		<description>Nestled under a sacred volcano, painted with waterfalls, rainbows, jungles, and flowers, sits Kauai's Hindu Monastery. A true place of peace. Here the sounds of the world fade away, until all that's left is the flowing river, singing birds, rippling leaves, and the resounding echo of the soul.</description>
